ca.bc.gov.open.cpf.api.domain

Interface BatchJobExecutionGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Common

    public interface BatchJobExecutionGroup
extends Common
    The BatchJobExecutionGroup represents a group of request to execute a BusinessApplication within a BatchJob. It contains the input and result data.
